The paper discusses the implementation of different Machine Learning algorithms to predict the overall equipment effectiveness (OEE) in a manufacturing industry. This falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of these algorithms to improve efficiency in the manufacturing industry, which falls under the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Computer Engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of these algorithms in the context of a specific industry, which falls under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
